longBusinessSummary: Graphex Group Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells graphene products in the People's Republic of China. It operates through three segments: Manufacturing and Sale of Graphene Products; Landscape Design; and The Catering Business Focuses on the Operation of Restaurants. The company provides spherical graphite and graphene for the use in electric vehicle batteries, lithium-ion batteries, advanced solar energy products, and other applications; high purity graphite for magnesia carbon bricks, high grade refractories, stabilizers, carbon brushes, and fire-resistant composite materials applications; and micronized graphite for corrosion-resistant coating, lubricants, and other composite materials applications. It also offers landscape architecture services urban renewals, corporate campuses, hotels/resorts, and theme parks projects for governments, property developers, design service companies, and engineering businesses. In addition, the company provides catering services, including the operation and management of Thai Gallery restaurants, which serves Thai cuisine. Further, it offers interior design and catering management services; and invests in food industry. The company was formerly known as Earthasia International Holdings Limited and changed its name to Graphex Group Limited in April 2021. Graphex Group Limited was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong.
